commit.message:
Merge pull request #3 from myhro/travis

Add Travis support

Add .cache to .gitignore.

Also remove unused local_config.py.
Move tests out of the package and remove tests/__init__.py.

Merge pull request #2 from myhro/fix-test-suite

Fix test suite to work with Python 3

Fix test suite to work with Python 3

* In Python 3, `map()` returns a map object, not a list, making the test
fail with `TypeError: can only concatenate list (not `map`) to list`.
* Python 3 doesn't have `basestring`, which was making another test
fail.

Fixes #1.
Add requirements to the example project.
Bugfix: Allow integer ports in split_address.
